  "subject": "Allow docker-golang-shell-daily to specify node",
  "commit_message": "Allow docker-golang-shell-daily to specify node\n\nAllow {project-name}-{stream}-docker-golang-shell-daily\nto allow a specific build-node to be able to run these\njobs using the ARM architecture nodes.\n\nAll current projects using this job will stay unchaged and\nwill still run their builds on ubuntu1604-docker-8c-8g.\n\nChange-Id: I9afacb764a9619aa2fdbc6371995be770a4b6bd4\nIssue-ID: CIMAN-219\nSigned-off-by: Paul Vaduva <Paul.Vaduva@enea.com>\n",
